Package org.hibernate.boot.spi

Interface EffectiveMappingDefaults

All Known Implementing Classes:
OverriddenMappingDefaults, RootMappingDefaults
public interface EffectiveMappingDefaults
Defaults which are in effect for each mapping. A combination of global settings and XML-specific settings
